data.description: Upgraded home in desirable Village Green neighborhood. This 4 bedrooms 2.5 bath home is filled with upgades. You're greeted by the custom stamped concrete driveway and beautiful front porch. Upon entering, the home has extensive tile, granite, hardwood floors thru-out. Updated kitchen, and a giant walk-in pantry and a living and family room downstairs. Upstairs are 4 large bedrooms, a utility room, and a master suite with a dreamy walk-in closet. The back yard has a nice oversized concrete patio that overlooks a beautiful backyard. The new playset even stays. Fantastic home with an even more fantastic price tag. Make it yours today!
